headline: Invesco Small Cap Value Fund Q3 2025 Performance Review
summary: Stock selection in materials was the largest contributor to relative performance. Stock selection in healthcare, energy, industrials and IT detracted from relative return.

headline: U.S. Managed Care Q3 2025 Earnings Recap: Costs Grow As ACA Worries Loom
summary: US managed care insurers' Q3 earnings season was characterized by higher medical costs amid political uncertainty surrounding extensions of the Affordable Care Act tax credits.
